font.div: Identity Access Management: Only authorized users are allowed to administrate the platform.

div.span: Route 53: Utilize registered DNS with hosted zones.

font.div: Private Certificate Manager: Issues certificates for secure communication.
Internet Gateway: Access to the platform from anywhere.
NAT Gateway: Access to the internet from the platform.
Application Load Balancer: Distributes the application traffic.
Auto Scaling Group: Manage Compute resources
EBS: Block storage for platform data.
RDS: Postgres DB for platform data.
Bedrock: Utilize the full set of Bedrock capabilities from LLMs to agents, flows, guardrails, knowledge base, etc.
Claude: Set of Antropic Claude Models via Bedrock.
Nova: Set of Nova Foundation Models

KEYCLOAK: Identity and access management solution
NATS: Messaging system for enabling plugins.
NATS AUTh CALLOUT: Handle the authorization for the NATS
FLUENTBIT: Enables logs and metrics collection.
AI/RUN UI: User interface for interacting with the platform.
AI/RUN API: Business logic, data processing, and API operations.
MERMAID: Mermaid code for workflow visualization
MCP CONNECT: Enables cloud-based AI services to communicate with MCP servers.
